values:
All I want to do is shut Billy the hell up.  What an annoying little poop head.  

I downloaded Halo beta 2.0.  It's the full freakin game.  Btw

I bought it.  I am Gandalf the white!

If I were gay, I'd have sex with Shea.  Get back to you on that one.  

I've been playing Grand Theft Auto: Vice City ALL DAY LONG!!!!!!!!!!!!!11

Today I went to Wendys.  I got a meal #4, biggie size.  It was really good until I ate the onions.  Somehow, the onions tasted like anthrax and made me cough up blood.  I don't like onions and onions dont like me.  

I woke up this morning and turned on my computer.  I was very bored, so I went to go *buy* the game "Silent Hill 2" and "NFS: Hot Pursuit 2".  NFS finished first so I played it first.  It was fun.  I have a few extra pairs of pants for when I play Silent Hill 2.

I wanted to buy a Hover-Disc.  HoverDisc: A large disc that hovers.  Need I say more?

I thought it was going to be $8 but it was $16.  The hover-disc will soon be mine.
